Name: Get Out! Snakes!
About the game: Get out! Snakes! It's a new way to play the famous 90's cell phone classic, now you're not the snake, you're the snake's target! Save your apple friends on an adventure with 5 different worlds that tell the story of how a heroic red apple, guardian of the green apple tree, saves green apples from a terrible snake attack! So ... save the apples before the snake attacks, but stay tuned, as you too can be attacked! Features: 5 different worlds with 5 levels each Singleplayer or multiplayer story mode 2 players battle mode Original songs Original characters Great repetition value
